data.description: Well maintained and ready for you to move in at closing! Make this Northwood gem your next home today. A large corner lot with a fenced in backyard makes this home perfect for entertaining guests or just relaxing on a nice sunny day. Inside, you can't miss the spacious 2 car garage, TWO comfortable living/family room areas, and recently remodeled kitchen (2019). Most appliances staying, don't miss out on this! - Title work pre-started through Chicago Title/ACT - REVIEWING ALL OFFERS SUBMITTED BY 3:00PM SUNDAY 5/9
